Samsung is offering massive discounts on great TVs in their Black Friday 2019 promotion. Black Friday takes place on 29 November, but Samsung is offering its deals in an extended sale from 26 November – 2 December 2019. The deals will be available at all Samsung stores nationwide. All deals are subject to availability while stocks last. These are the best Samsung Black Friday TV deals. Click here for the location of your closest Samsung Store. <img class="size-large wp-image-330055 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-2-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-2-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-2-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-large wp-image-330053 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-1-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-1-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-1-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-large wp-image-330203 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/640x430_82_UHD-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/640x430_82_UHD.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/640x430_82_UHD-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/640x430_82_UHD-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-